| Device                    | Role                                                                                                                                       |
| ------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Raspberry Pi 5**        | Main SLAM processing unit (OAK-D Lite), evaluates SLAM quality, sends commands to PixRacer via ESP-01, and transfers files to Pi Zero 2 W. |
| **PixRacer**              | Controls all servos based on commands from Pi 5 via ESPNow (via onboard ESP8266).                                                          |
                               
üìÅ Folder Structure Assumption:
SLAM data folder: /home/pi/slam_data/

File format: .ply or .xyz or similar

ESP-01 connected via USB or GPIO as serial (/dev/ttyUSB0)

Pi Zero 2 W reachable via static IP (192.168.4.2) or ESPNow                            
